function Start()

-- Enable Wave 01 spawners.	
	for i, idSpawner in ipairs(tWave01) do
		if Hydra.ActorIsValid(idSpawner) then
			Hydra.ActorGizmoSetDisabled(idSpawner, false)
		end
	end	
	
end

function Start(idActorKiller, idActorKilled)
	
	-- Frenzy the minis when a bell dies.	
	Hydra.ActorTriggerPowerAtFeet(idActorKilled, S_POWER_MINI_FRENZY)

	-- Bell kill count.
	nBellKillCount = nBellKillCount + 1
	
	-- Add additional spawns when the first bell in the timmed phase has been destroyed.
	if nBellKillCount == 1 then
		for i, idSpawner in ipairs(tWave02) do
			if Hydra.ActorIsValid(idSpawner) then
				Hydra.ActorGizmoSetDisabled(idSpawner, false)
			end
		end	
	end
		
	-- Add additional spawns when the 3rd bell has been destroyed.
	if nBellKillCount == 3 then
		for i, idSpawner in ipairs(tWave03) do
			if Hydra.ActorIsValid(idSpawner) then
				Hydra.ActorGizmoSetDisabled(idSpawner, false)
			end
		end	
	end
	
end

function Start(szGroup)

-- Enable reward chest.
	if Hydra.ActorIsValid(idChestRare) then
		Hydra.ActorGizmoSetDisabled(idChestRare, false)
	end

end

function Start()

	-- Disable all remaining Spawners
	for i, idAllSpawner in ipairs(tAllSpawners) do
		if Hydra.ActorIsValid(idAllSpawner) then
			Hydra.ActorGizmoSetDisabled(idAllSpawner, true)
		end
	end
end
